<li id="c77">
  <div class="cx" id="cx50294182">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">How do you know?</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1212198/50294182#c77?mode=alone;showrate=1#c77">2+ / 0-</a>)</span>
